 CIRCULAR”</a></p>\r\n          </div>\r\n        </a>\r\n\t  </div>\r\n\t  <div class=\"bl_card\">\r\n        <a class=\"bl_card\" href=\"/sustainability/vision/world03/index.html\">\r\n          <figure class=\"cardImg\">\r\n            <img class=\"lazyload\" data-src=\"/sustainability/images/future_03.png\" alt=\"\">\r\n          </figure>\r\n          <div class=\"cardBody\">\r\n            <h3 class=\"heading\">誰もが安全な水・空気を利用し、<br>自然環境が回復した世界</h3>\r\n          </div>\r\n        </a>\r\n\t  </div>\r\n\t  <div class=\"bl_card\">\r\n        <a class=\"bl_card\" href=\"/sustainability/vision/world04/index.html\">\r\n          <figure class=\"cardImg\">\r\n            <img class=\"lazyload\" data-src=\"/sustainability/images/future_04.png\" alt=\"\">\r\n          </figure>\r\n          <div class=\"cardBody\">\r\n            <h3 class=\"heading\">すべての人が健康で衛生的な<br>生活を送る世界</h3>\r\n          </div>\r\n        </a>\r\n\t  </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"bl_btnWrap\">\r\n      <a class=\"el_btn -wide\" href=\"/sustainability/\">サステナビリティ</a>\r\n    </div>\r\n\r\n  </div>\r\n</div>--><!-- /ly_container-->\r\n\r\n<div class=\"ly_container\">\r\n  <div class=\"ly_inner _pb0\">  \r\n    <div class=\"uq_topAthlete\">\r\n    <div class=\"ly_inner\">\r\n      <div class=\"bl_sectionHeading _mt0 _mb10\">\r\n        <h2 class=\"heading\"><span>選手の最新の競技情報や東レとのパートナーシップへの思い、<br class=\"_pcShow\">メッセージやインタビューなどサニブラウン本人の素顔に迫ります。</span></h2>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div class=\"outline\">\r\n        <div class=\"bl_btnWrap\">\r\n          <a class=\"el_btn -wide\" href=\"/partnership/athlete/\" target=\"_blank\">もっと見る</a>\r\n        </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n    \r\n  </div>\r\n</div><!-- /ly_container-->\r\n\r\n <div class=\"ly_container\">\r\n  <div class=\"ly_inner _pt0\">  \r\n    <div class=\"uq_topThatswhy\">\r\n    <div class=\"ly_inner\">\r\n      <div class=\"bl_sectionHeading _mt0\">\r\n        <h2 class=\"heading\">だから、東レ。<span>～That's Wh